  "decision_conditions": [
    "The Planning Inspectorate allow the appeal and grant planning permission for addition of mansard roof extension to match adjacent houses at 99 Cloudesley Road, London, N1 0EN in accordance with the terms of the application (Ref. P040669) dated 18th March 2004 and the plans submitted therewith, subject to the following conditions:\r\n\r\n1. The development hereby permitted shall be begun before the expiration of five years from the date of this permission.\r\n\r\n2.  No development shall take place until samples of the materials to be used in the construction of the external surfaces of the extension hereby permitted have been submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority.  Development shall be carried out in accordance with the approved details.\r\n\r\n3.  No development shall take place until drawings of an appropriate scale showing details of dormer windows and rooflight, including all window joinery details and the relationship of the frames to the openings have been submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority.  The development shall be carried out in accordance with the approved details."
